i\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我未飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你飲過邊d好既介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成罐/包就買過金天閣抹茶粉(茶之環), 四方之薰(山政小山園)同Tomiz京都宇治抹茶<br />\n金天閣濃茶薄茶都啱, 有茶香, 鮮味同回甘, 濃茶有啲苦但係接受到<br />\n四方之薰茶香唔及金天閣(都有可能係我擺耐咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 薄茶OK但係濃茶太澀<br />\nTomiz冇茶香同茶味更加唔好講回甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇味到沖濃茶都唔會苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前出街飲過中村藤吉濃茶同薄茶, 香味, 濃郁度同鮮味勁過金天閣好多, 不過佢用嘅粉起碼二百幾一罐唔出奇<br />\n抹茶館冇印象<br />\n京林屋都係嗰句, 可一不可再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊想試辻利茶舖梅之白同丸久小山園雲鶴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係未有閒錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n金天閣可以係樂天買到？我諗住買完送去我香港地址 我屋企人再帶過黎 廢事佢地出去買"},{"pid":"52dbd97b488f1d594c572927414c584fc673341a","tid":240575,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:58:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打又玩酒又玩抹茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日俾屋企人話如果啲心機時間(同$)攞去做正經嘢<br />\n博士都讀咗返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返緊份萬零蚊頽工月月清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時教我玩抹茶呀大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我其實真係想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我完全唔係用茶道正宗方法沖(沖茶前後都好撚多嘢要準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n用熱水開粉再用茶筅刷到起泡就淨飲or配甜食<br />\n單純學薄茶/濃茶點沖嘅話中村藤吉個官網有教<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/tea_matcha.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tokichi.jp%2Fchinese_traditional%2Ftea%2Ftea_matcha.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=96b5c55e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/tea_matcha.html</a><br />\nMIYABI就詳細啲, 有講點揀抹茶粉<br />\n<a href=\"http://miyabi-taiwan.blogspot.hk/2011/03/blog-post_4013.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmiyabi-taiwan.blogspot.hk%2F2011%2F03%2Fblog-post_4013.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=1e49dc8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://miyabi-taiwan.blogspot.hk/2011/03/blog-post_4013.html</a><br />\n胖狗過生活最詳細, 基本上就係教茶道沖茶嗰部份<br />\n<a href=\"http://fatdoglife.blogspot.hk/2014/11/blog-post_14.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffatdoglife.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F11%2Fblog-post_14.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=eaa48734\" target=\"_blank\">http://fatdoglife.blogspot.hk/2014/11/blog-post_14.html</a><br />\n我都係睇呢幾個網學返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成套茶道直頭係儀式嚟, 由茶室佈置, 進入茶室嘅方法, 準備茶具, 到正式沖茶, 點樣由主人家分菓子同茶俾客人, 客人點樣飲茶(提示: 唔可以攞起茶碗就咁飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 傾乜話題...總之好撚多禮節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對茶道認真有興趣可以睇&quot;日本茶道裏千家教室&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://urasenketw.tian.yam.com/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Furasenketw.tian.yam.com%2Fposts&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=1c598b62\" target=\"_blank\">http://urasenketw.tian.yam.com/posts</a><br />\n(個網站設計好濕鳩, 㩒右邊&quot;分類篩選&quot;個tag睇menu)<br />\nblog主去過日本拜師, 學成返台灣開班教學, 係正規嘅裏千家茶道先生<br />\n<br />\n香港正式嘅就有&quot;茶道裏千家淡交會香港協會&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://urasenkehk.jimdo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Furasenkehk.jimdo.com%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=e653835f\" target=\"_blank\">https://urasenkehk.jimdo.com/</a><br />\nCityU有間&quot;友香庵&quot;, 都係正宗茶道, 好似有guided tour"},{"pid":"8a4ce34e20a49cc64abbd3c4a575d00dde7379af","tid":240575,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:12:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>講埋飲抹茶<br />\n香港依家多咗地方有正式抹茶飲<br />\n最平應該係抹茶館, 茶粉, 茶碗同茶筅連一壺熱水, 有說明書教點沖, 埋單加一都係廿零蚊<br />\n銅鑼灣刨冰舖之前飲過幾次, 五六十蚊抹茶套餐有一碗茶連一件和菓子, 好似唔係自己沖, 同埋耐冇幫襯唔知個套餐仲喺唔喺度<br />\n貴嘅就中村藤吉(餐廳嗰邊), 有得嗌薄茶或者濃茶, 一碗茶加一兩件和菓子(好似仲有醃菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 又係百幾二百<br />\n京林屋試過一次, 可一不可再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去過希慎分店一次, 二百幾一碗茶(俾多一百唔夠就買到同店30g茶粉), 茶色仲要少少黃, 茶粉又唔夠新鮮</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 多謝絲打介紹得咁仔細 即係如果沖黎飲就買靚少少既薄茶就ok? 我聽講係咪有隻牌子叫一保堂 性格比幾好？其實我依家係澳洲 遲下屋企人黎 想叫佢帶幾罐俾我</blockquote><br />\n性價比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n濃茶用抹茶粉沖濃茶, 薄茶都得<br />\n薄茶粉沖濃茶就唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以唔飲濃茶只飲薄茶買返薄茶用茶粉就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我都係為興趣得閒飲吓咁, 買咗幾罐都係香港有賣嘅抹茶粉<br />\n一保堂未見過香港有賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n港台有介紹, 都係百年老店, 應該唔會太差?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我未飲過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你飲過邊d好既介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成罐/包就買過金天閣抹茶粉(茶之環), 四方之薰(山政小山園)同Tomiz京都宇治抹茶<br />\n金天閣濃茶薄茶都啱, 有茶香, 鮮味同回甘, 濃茶有啲苦但係接受到<br />\n四方之薰茶香唔及金天閣(都有可能係我擺耐咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 薄茶OK但係濃茶太澀<br />\nTomiz冇茶香同茶味更加唔好講回甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇味到沖濃茶都唔會苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好耐之前出街飲過中村藤吉濃茶同薄茶, 香味, 濃郁度同鮮味勁過金天閣好多, 不過佢用嘅粉起碼二百幾一罐唔出奇<br />\n抹茶館冇印象<br />\n京林屋都係嗰句, 可一不可再<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嚟緊想試辻利茶舖梅之白同丸久小山園雲鶴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係未有閒錢買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n金天閣可以係樂天買到？我諗住買完送去我香港地址 我屋企人再帶過黎 廢事佢地出去買</blockquote><br />\n啱啱去樂天搵過冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過有丸久小山園抹茶 (就係之前香港某間俾人屌到化嘅抹茶甜品舖代理嘅牌子)<br />\n樂天市集有幾間舖賣呢隻抹茶, 大部份都平過香港門市, 不過最好睇埋運費同匯率抵唔抵, 尤其呢排日元比起早兩個月又升返少少<br />\n仲有香港抹茶舖賣嘅茶具套裝都係有返咁上下質素(真係for正式茶道場合), 初學/自用套裝去樂天市場搵平好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54043a3669e38aa3d37eec55c16800d3effc9757","tid":240575,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:17:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打又玩酒又玩抹茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日俾屋企人話如果啲心機時間(同$)攞去做正經嘢<br />\n博士都讀咗返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返緊份萬零蚊頽工月月清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時教我玩抹茶呀大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我其實真係想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我完全唔係用茶道正宗方法沖(沖茶前後都好撚多嘢要準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n用熱水開粉再用茶筅刷到起泡就淨飲or配甜食<br />\n單純學薄茶/濃茶點沖嘅話中村藤吉個官網有教<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/tea_matcha.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tokichi.jp%2Fchinese_traditional%2Ftea%2Ftea_matcha.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=96b5c55e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/tea_matcha.html</a><br />\nMIYABI就詳細啲, 有講點揀抹茶粉<br />\n<a href=\"http://miyabi-taiwan.blogspot.hk/2011/03/blog-post_4013.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmiyabi-taiwan.blogspot.hk%2F2011%2F03%2Fblog-post_4013.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=1e49dc8e\" target=\"_blank\">http://miyabi-taiwan.blogspot.hk/2011/03/blog-post_4013.html</a><br />\n胖狗過生活最詳細, 基本上就係教茶道沖茶嗰部份<br />\n<a href=\"http://fatdoglife.blogspot.hk/2014/11/blog-post_14.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffatdoglife.blogspot.hk%2F2014%2F11%2Fblog-post_14.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=eaa48734\" target=\"_blank\">http://fatdoglife.blogspot.hk/2014/11/blog-post_14.html</a><br />\n我都係睇呢幾個網學返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n成套茶道直頭係儀式嚟, 由茶室佈置, 進入茶室嘅方法, 準備茶具, 到正式沖茶, 點樣由主人家分菓子同茶俾客人, 客人點樣飲茶(提示: 唔可以攞起茶碗就咁飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />), 傾乜話題...總之好撚多禮節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n對茶道認真有興趣可以睇&quot;日本茶道裏千家教室&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"http://urasenketw.tian.yam.com/posts\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Furasenketw.tian.yam.com%2Fposts&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=1c598b62\" target=\"_blank\">http://urasenketw.tian.yam.com/posts</a><br />\n(個網站設計好濕鳩, 㩒右邊&quot;分類篩選&quot;個tag睇menu)<br />\nblog主去過日本拜師, 學成返台灣開班教學, 係正規嘅裏千家茶道先生<br />\n<br />\n香港正式嘅就有&quot;茶道裏千家淡交會香港協會&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://urasenkehk.jimdo.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Furasenkehk.jimdo.com%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=e653835f\" target=\"_blank\">https://urasenkehk.jimdo.com/</a><br />\nCityU有間&quot;友香庵&quot;, 都係正宗茶道, 好似有guided tour</blockquote><br />\n絲打好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n幾時一齊交流下<br />\n我教你玩手沖咖啡呀<br />\n俾你入多個坑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"237c45f18205fb64511dba918659a627b67d427a","tid":240575,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:32:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>絲打又玩酒又玩抹茶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n成日俾屋企人話如果啲心機時間(同$)攞去做正經嘢<br />\n博士都讀咗返嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n返緊份萬零蚊頽工月月清<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾時教我玩抹茶呀大師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我其實真係想學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我完全唔係用茶道正宗方法沖(沖茶前後都好撚多嘢要準備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n用熱水開粉再用茶筅刷到起泡就淨飲or配甜食<br />\n單純學薄茶/濃茶點沖嘅話中村藤吉個官網有教<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/tea_matcha.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tokichi.jp%2Fchinese_traditional%2Ftea%2Ftea_matcha.html&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FJUJf0bKPU4tHf%2BJg0Yv85M%3D&h=96b5c55e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tokichi.jp/chinese_traditional/tea/tea_matcha.html</a